title: #65 - Logan Paul Slammed On Twitter & Ethan Quits Social Media
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila return from their week in social media exile! Together we discuss Logan Paul and Chris D'Elia's twitter spat, we listen to voice mails, Hila sends the news, and we are joined in the studio by Chaos Chaos for a musical performance!
